CYSTIC
FIBROSIS
WAS
EVALUATED
SEVENTYONE
PERCENT
OF
PATIENTS
TREATED
WITH
TICARCILLIN
ALONE
RESPONDED
FAVORABLY
THE
RESPONSE
RATE
WAS
SIMILAR
IN
